<concept id="concept_804F9A67161447579091BF818BDF0A5E">
  <title>Validating a Targeted Campaign</title>
  <shortdesc>After you create a targeted campaign, you should verify that it
	 works as expected. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <conbody>
    <p>Begin with the 
		<xref href="c_Campaign_Quality_Assurance.xml#concept_B645EA1BB55149E4AB8328F9943AC86A" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local">Campaign Quality Assurance
		  Process</xref>. 
	 </p>
    <p>For each experience mimic each type of targeting situation in your
		campaign. This includes 
		<b>meeting</b>, and 
		<b>not meeting</b> the targeting conditions. 
	 </p>
  </conbody>
